Name: Bouquets
Short description: Our bouquets are handcrafted for your occasion
Description: Are you planning a special occasion? Choose one of our amazing bouquets made for your special day. We use only the best locally grown flowers to make bouquets that will look great.

Name: Herbs
Short description: Fresh smelling herbs can add a freshness to any room
Description: We often think of herbs for cooking, but herbs such as lavendar, rosemary, and sage can be used in bouquets to give a room an earthy feel.

Name: Proteas
Description: These champions of the Cape floral kingdom give  wonderful colours and unique foliage.

Name: Purple Passion
Description: Looking to make a statement? Choose Purple Passion to brighten your day.

Name: Roses
Description: Roses are beautiful and well-loved for a reason. We choose roses not only for looks, but also for scent.

Name: Simple Colour
Description: Our 'simple colour' flowers are based on what is in season and what we know will be able to stand alone and make an impact.

Name: Summer Sensation
Description: Our original Summer Sensation bouquets celebrate the best of summer in all its glories.

Name: Wild and Free
Description: Our Wild and Free bouquets add a dash of chaos and beauty. They emphasise light and air.
